=C2=A0

Hosts Vladimir Duthiers, Gayle King, and Tony Dokoupil asked about Trump, h=
is swift crackdown on illegal immigrants, the threat of tariffs, and the go=
vernor=E2=80=99s take on the state of the Democratic Party. Whitmer, an occ=
asionally
