helon=E2=80=99s poll after the November election. Trump=E2=80=99s favorable=
 rating is also now 10 points higher than Biden=E2=80=99s=E2=80=94and two p=
oints higher than that of Kamala Harris, his ultimate opponent last year.

=C2=A0

Trump=E2=80=99s best issue with voters=E2=80=94perhaps no
