ans like Elon Musk, Meta=E2=80=99s Mark Zuckerberg, Amazon=E2=80=99s Jeff B=
ezos, OpenAI=E2=80=99s Sam Altman,
Google=E2=80=99s Sundar Pichai, and TikTok=E2=80=99s Shou Zi Chew.=C2=A0

=C2=A0

Most Americans are uneasy about Trump cozying up to the Silicon Valley set =
